                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Using a Heavy Attack on a melee weapon with this equipped will deplete the Combo Counter like usual, but it will then rapidly regenerate to full within 2 seconds."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Corrupt Charge",
                  "pageId": 233707,
                  "revisionId": 2663912,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The Combo Duration penalty is calculated from the melee weapon's base value. Meaning it always subtracts exactly 2.5 seconds and therefore is easily counteracted by Body Count and/or Drifting Contact ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
