                  "revisionId": 2663912,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "It is possible to make a weapon's constant heavy attack speed faster than the regeneration rate, such as with a combination of Killing Blow , Amalgam Organ Shatter and one of Fury or Berserker Fury , or simply have a naturally very fast weapon."
